    <item>
      <title>中石油钻井强劲 上半年创纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/petrochina-s-strong-drilling-results-lead-to-record-first-half</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于高钻井产量和坚挺的油价帮助中国石油抵御了中国燃料需求疲软的影响，中国石油股份有限公司公布了今年上半年创纪录的收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/petrochina-s-strong-drilling-results-lead-to-record-first-half</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 11:19:27 GMT</pubDate>
